    <string name="disclaimer_texto">This application has been developed for educational and informational purposes, and is intended as a guiding tool for calculating Body Mass Index (BMI) in both adults and minors.

MEDICAL AND PROFESSIONAL USE
• Does not replace the opinion of a healthcare professional.
• Calculated values and interpretations provided are approximate and should not be considered medical diagnoses.
• In case of health concerns, always consult with a doctor or pediatrician.

ABOUT MINORS
• BMI calculation in minors is based on WHO references.
• Childhood BMI is not interpreted the same as in adults. This application is not designed to evaluate development in children under 5 years.

PRIVACY AND SECURITY
• This application does not collect or transmit personal data to external servers.
• All information is stored locally on the device, without encryption. It is recommended not to enter sensitive personal data.

USER RESPONSIBILITY
• The user is solely responsible for the use of this application.</string>
